            "text": ", which was accompanied by over 80 other vehicle lots in a special Kiwi auction. Some people couldn’t believe that such an exotic-looking and once-desirable Lotus was estimated to sell for only $35,000 to $40,000. Surely there was a mistake, they all wondered.",
