      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "And then the auction came and went, the car going for $37,375. That’s about in the middle of the estimated range, for those who aren’t so good at math. In other words, if you want a cool supercar from the 80s, you might want to consider the Lotus Esprit.",
