        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2021/01/Lotus-Esprit-New-Zealand-3.jpg",
        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080,
        "caption": "photo credit: Webb's"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Lotus Esprits are kind of the forgotten supercars of yesteryear, at least when it comes to collectors. That means they don’t go for prices which are out of reach for everyone except the extremely wealthy. You can’t say the same for something like the Lamborghini Countach or Ferrari F40.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
